Source: pg-typescript
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), cargo, clang
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/isaacd9/pg_typescript

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-typescript
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-typescript
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: TypeScript procedural language extension for PostgreSQL
 pg_typescript adds a trusted TypeScript procedural language to PostgreSQL,
 powered by Deno and V8. It supports TypeScript functions, controlled runtime
 permissions, remote import maps, and callbacks into PostgreSQL for
 PostgreSQL 16 through 18.
